  "intent": "Execute the Omega Mag-Bind\u00ae Total RNA 96 Kit extraction protocol for 96 samples using magnetic bead-based purification. Begin with binding buffer addition (320\u00b5L) and magnetic separation, followed by sequential wash steps with VHB buffer (400\u00b5L), RNA wash buffers (400\u00b5L and 300\u00b5L), DNase treatment (52\u00b5L with 10-minute incubation), and PHM buffer treatment (150\u00b5L). Complete the protocol with final elution using 70\u00b5L elution buffer transferred to a temperature-controlled aluminum block at 4\u00b0C. All transfers use P300 multi-channel pipette with tip parking between steps and magnetic deck engagement for bead separation.",
